	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.ouya.tv/">http://www.ouya.tv/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Thought I'd post this up for anyone who hasn't seen this yet.  Having an emu on this thing could present a decent opportunity to release homebrew NES games without (or in addition to) the hassles of cartridge release.  Or even a full out console game for those interested in more hardware than the NES has to offer.  Pretty cool to see this thing being supported so well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


