		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's designed with ease of modding ind mind (both hw and sw). It's &quot;locked&quot; because they want to reach a wide audience of less techy users unlike us. That will help in building a large user base of both developers and gamers. A console with specific hardware and controllers that is easy to pick up and plug in and play, and easy to develop for. I think it's a great idea. Of course there are other android based devices, and noone is stopping anyone from developing more.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
